---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const effectiveDate = '2026-05-17';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy | MindMotion"
  description="How MindMotion handles information collected through this website."
>
  <Nav />
  <main id="main">
    <Section heading="Privacy policy">
      <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> {effectiveDate}</p>
      <p>
        MindMotion, Inc. ("MindMotion", "we", "our") operates this website.
        This policy describes what information the website collects, how it is
        used, and the third parties involved in processing it.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Information collected">
      <p>
        <strong>Cookieless analytics.</strong> The site uses Cloudflare Web
        Analytics, which does not set tracking cookies and does not require
        visitor consent under GDPR or CCPA. The service collects aggregate,
        anonymous information about page visits.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Contact form submissions.</strong> When you submit the contact
        form, we collect the information you provide: first name, last name,
        work email, organization, role, and message.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Scheduling.</strong> If you book a meeting via a scheduling
        link, the scheduling tool's host processes your booking information
        (name, email, time slot). This applies only when a scheduling link
        is in use.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="How information is used">
      <p>
        We use contact-form submissions to respond to your inquiry. We use
        aggregate analytics to understand site usage. We do not sell your
        information or share it with third parties for marketing.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Third-party processors">
      <p>The following services process information on our behalf:</p>
      <p>
        <strong>Cloudflare</strong> &mdash; web analytics. Cookieless and
        anonymous in aggregate.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Web3Forms</strong> &mdash; receives contact-form submissions
        and delivers them to our team's inbox.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Scheduling tool host</strong> &mdash; processes meeting
        bookings when a scheduling link is in use.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Cookies">
      <p>
        The site sets no first-party tracking cookies. Cloudflare Web
        Analytics does not require cookies. No cookie banner is displayed
        because no consent is required. If this changes (for example, if
        third-party embeds that set cookies are added later) a banner will be
        added at that time.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Retention">
      <p>
        We retain contact-form submissions only as long as needed to respond
        to your inquiry, typically no longer than twelve months.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Your rights">
      <p>
        If you are in the EU, UK, or California, you may have rights to
        access, correct, or delete information we hold about you. To make a
        request, use the <a href="/contact">contact form</a>. We do not list a
        public email address; the contact form is the canonical channel.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Updates">
      <p>
        We may update this policy. The effective date above reflects the
        latest revision.
      </p>
    </Section>

    <Section heading="Contact">
      <p>
        Questions about this policy: use the
        <a href="/contact">contact form</a>.
      </p>
    </Section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
